sql_query.sql:
SELECT "users".* FROM "users" INNER JOIN "topic_users" ON "topic_users"."user_id" = "users"."id" WHERE (users.id > 0) AND (NOT EXISTS(
                     SELECT 1
                     FROM anonymous_users a
                     WHERE a.user_id = users.id
                  )) AND "users"."staged" = FALSE AND "users"."id" != 1741 AND "topic_users"."last_read_post_number" IS NOT NULL AND (topic_users.topic_id = 1134 AND topic_users.last_read_post_number >= 3) AND (admin OR moderator)
